EditorialReview.Content:
This is a great gatsby cap sleeve maxi floor dress.The shoulder part is the tulle with sequin leaves,elegant but sexy.From the sweetheart bust to knee,it is covered with the black sequin lucky clovers,brings you lucky and happiness.The trumpet hemline is the mesh fabric,it hangs like waterfall,shows your golden ratio figure .Attending 1920s themed wedding ,or going to a evening party/company party,this dress will shows the best and the most beautiful of you.

Please understand this dress run a little large,the accurate size should be :(The tag size is the size label in the dress)Tag XS for US 2/4,Tag S for US 6/8,Tag M for US 10/12,Tag L for US 14/16,Tag XL for US 18/20,Tag XXL for US 20/22.

Please notice :the color "Champagne "is in champagne sequin,the color "gold beige" is in gold sequin.
